0.title: Consolation Needed
0.query:
timeseries needed = avg(vmware.vm.consolidation.needed), by: { `dt.entity.vmware:virtualmachine` }
| fieldsAdd entityName(`dt.entity.vmware:virtualmachine`)
| sort arrayAvg(needed) desc
| limit 20
